messages.message:
I do have a question for Rel Eng team. Hopefully I can join next office hours.

Q:  I am looking to setup private one-way connectivity between  Jenkins AWS EC2 Runners/workers and Sandbox VPCs.  I would like to know the the current networking setup for Jenkins preprod.

Happy to walk through it over a huddle some time, but the workers are spawned into this VPC (https://us-east-2.console.aws.amazon.com/vpc/home?region=us-east-2#vpcs:VpcId=vpc-04b4b81ad251ce59a;sort=VpcId) (instabase-dev acct, ID vpc-04b4b81ad251ce59a), specifically this subnet (https://us-east-2.console.aws.amazon.com/vpc/home?region=us-east-2#SubnetDetails:subnetId=subnet-081c8e44af2a28a9f) (public, ID subnet-081c8e44af2a28a9f)
